milestones.description: Brian Lara has become the top scorer for WI in ODIs with 8671 runs, going past Haynes's 8648

stories.title: West Indies race to seven-wicket win
stories.subTitle: England v West Indies, NatWest Series, Trent Bridge
stories.summary: An unbeaten half-century from Chris Gayle anchored West Indies to a comfortable seven-wicket win over England at Trent Bridge after an impressive bowling display by West Indies meant that England set them a target of only 148 to win
stories.byline: The Wisden Bulletin by Liam Brickhill

stories.title: Rain has the final say
